Class QAKParser

java.lang.Object

StructureParser
@Produces(segment="QAK", resource=org.hl7.fhir.r4.model.OperationOutcome.class) public class QAKParser extends AbstractSegmentParser
Parser for QAK Segments The QAK segment populates OperationOutcome.issue referenced by any generated MessageHeader.response.details with the code from QAK-2 field.
